Charles Inslee https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Charles_Inslee 0 Charles E. Inslee (1870 – September 1922) was an American actor. He appeared in 127 films between 1908 and 1921. He first acted in films in 1908, and found work with the Edison, Biograph, Bison and Kalem studios.He was born in New York City in 1870. He died in September 1922.
